Ventral abdomen with yellow and dark areas anteriorly to posteriorly. Dorsal connexivum with a dark spot occupying about 1 / 3 of each segment, wider on anterior portion, and narrowing towards posterior portion. Internal and external borders of connexivum with a noncontinuous yellow stripe. Externally yellow stripe not continuous. First abdominal segment resembling metasternum, but smaller (
